posting_body: ['CONTACT COREY for MORE INFO, PICS', 'TEXT CODE: 22165977 & your name to', 'show contact info', 'Or call or email me', "IF THIS PLACE DOESN'T FIT,", 'ASK ABOUT OUR EXTENSIVE LIST OF', 'OTHER PROPERTIES / RENT / BUY / SELL /', 'LUXURY ESTATES / HOUSES /', 'COMMERCIAL / APARTMENTS', "*and we'll assist you through the entire process!*", '$4,900 House For Rent 1 Year+', '4 Beds', '3 Baths', '2,032 SqFt', 'Prime Encino Park location just minutes away from great food and entertainment along Ventura Blvd, and close to the ever so popular Balboa Park and Sports Complex, this updated house is now available for you to call home.', 'You will enjoy the spacious and open layout that is just perfect for relaxing with friends and family, or for entertaining guests.', 'As you enter the home, you will have the option to lounge in the formal living room or continue on to the great room with kitchen, family room and dining area, all leading out to the backyard.', 'The kitchen has plenty of storage and countertops, making it ideal for any home cook.', 'All bedrooms are on one wing of the house with the primary bedroom situate in the back, offering much needed privacy, along with direct access to the backyard.', 'The large closet provides the space needed for your clothes and to get ready for the day.', 'The special en-suite bathroom truly makes this bedroom its own oasis.', 'Plenty of natural light floods this beautiful home throughout.', "Don't wait on this one.", 'It will go fast.', '***Please Text Code: 22165977 & your name to', 'show contact info', 'For Details & Pictures***', 'And check out my website: <URL>/', 'Brought to you by Corey Trevor at Los Angeles Area - eXp Realty of California, Inc.', 'CA DRE#01878277']
